				<h3>Regarding Indian Scripts in Java Web Application</h3>
				<div class="postmsg">
					<p>Hi Mr Gopi,<br /><br />I am Vijay Kumar Working as a Software Engineer in Bangalore.<br /><br />I am a starter in Developing Java based web applications.Now i am building a web application using struts.<br />I have successfully done for applying i18n to&nbsp; French,German,Spanish Languages.<br /><br />Now I am trying for Indian based script languages.Telugu,Tamil,etc.<br />I am using ResuorceBundle,Locale,Properties files and&nbsp; Unicode.<br /><br />When&nbsp; I am trying to display Telugu using Unicode it is Displaying ????????s (question marks and boxes).<br />can you please help me on this.<br /><br />Thank you for contributing your valuable time.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="postsignature"><hr />Thanks&amp;Regards,<br />Vijay Kumar,<br />Software Engineer.</div>
			</div>
